EN: The victory in this battle requires everyone to unite as one.

ZH: 通过磨练自己的技能，他终于成为了一名顶级的选手。
EN: By honing his skills, he finally became a top player.

ZH: 这次考试的成功需要每个学生都认真准备。
EN: Success in this exam requires every student to prepare seriously.

ZH: 他的成功离不开家人的支持和鼓励。
EN: His success is inseparable from the support and encouragement of his family.
